p.strong: Doubly-Linked List for Buffer Pool Eviction

ul.li: Page 2 is in middle of list
Most recently used → Least recently used

ol.li:
Remove Page 2 from current position
Update neighbors' pointers

Insert at HEAD
Page 2 → prev = NULL
Page 2 → next = old HEAD
old HEAD → prev = Page 2
If dirty: write to disk first
Frame is now free for new page
